# Bellabeat Case Study (Fitbit Data Analysis)

[ðŸ“„ Click here to view the full report (PDF)]()

This case study explores how smart device data can help Bellabeat, a wellness-focused company, understand user behavior and improve its marketing strategy.

## Tools Used
- RStudio
- Excel
- Power BI
- Google Sheets (for cleaning)

## Process Overview
- Data cleaning and transformation
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
- Visualization and storytelling
- Business recommendations

## Key Insights
- Most users are less active during weekends.
- Majority of tracked users fall below the recommended activity level.
- High correlation between activity levels and sleep quality.

## Conclusion
The Bellabeat team can improve their device engagement by targeting underactive users and promoting features related to sleep and wellness routines.

